15 FALSE PRETENSES CHANGES
16 SECTION 10.2.(a) G.S. 42-59(2) reads as rewritten:
17 "(2) "Criminal activity" means (i) activity that would constitute a violation of
18 G.S. 90-95 other than a violation of G.S. 90-95(a)(3), or a conspiracy to
19 violate any provision of G.S. 90-95 other than G.S. 90-95(a)(3); or (ii) other
20 criminal activity that threatens the health, safety, or right of peaceful
21 enjoyment of the entire premises by other residents or employees of the
22 landlord.landlord; or (iii) obtaining rental property or other lodging by use of
